var cachePush = require('./cachePush'), getNative = require('./getNative'); /** Native method references. */ var Set = getNative(global, 'Set'); /* Native method references for those with the same name as other `lodash` methods. */ var nativeCreate = getNative(Object, 'create'); /** * * Creates a cache object to store unique values. * * @private * @param {Array} [values] The values to cache. */ function SetCache(values) { var length = values ? values.length : 0; this.data = { 'hash': nativeCreate(null), 'set': new Set }; while (length--) { this.push(values[length]); } } // Add functions to the `Set` cache. SetCache.prototype.push = cachePush; module.exports = SetCache;
